(Key Manager \(Atho\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Status: Alpha documentation snapshot \(2026-03-12\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This note explains how Atho?s key manager stores, loads, and uses keys for wallets, mining) Tj
T*
(rewards, and API authentication.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(What it does) Tj
T*
(- Generates Falcon-512 keypairs for wallet/miner addresses.) Tj
T*
(- Defaults to mnemonic-backed deterministic key generation \(atho-mnemonic-v1\) with 24 words) Tj
T*
(\(12/24/48 supported\).) Tj
T*
(- Derives hashed public keys \(HPK\) and Base56 addresses for display/UX.) Tj
T*
(- Persists keys atomically to Keys/KeyManager_Public_Private_Keys.json \(one file per) Tj
T*
(node/instance\).) Tj
T*
(- Supplies keys to transaction signing, mining coinbase outputs, and API auth where needed.) Tj
T*
(- Imports existing Falcon keys \(see below\) with hash/base56 verification and a test-sign before) Tj
T*
(storing.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Storage layout) Tj
T*
(- Path \(by default\): Keys/KeyManager_Public_Private_Keys.json) Tj
T*
(- Structure:) Tj
T*
(- miner_1, miner_2, ?: labels for each managed key.) Tj
T*
(- public_key: Falcon public key \(stored as 2048-char hex in key files\).) Tj
T*
(- private_key: Falcon private key components \(F, G, f, g\).) Tj
T*
(- mnemonic_phrase, mnemonic_words, mnemonic_text, mnemonic_meta for mnemonic-derived keys.) Tj
T*
(- Metadata: creation time, role \(e.g., miner\), network.) Tj
T*
(- Files are written atomically to avoid partial writes and corruption.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Encrypted-at-rest lockbox mode) Tj
T*
(- Key file now supports encrypted-at-rest mode with one-password unlock flow.) Tj
T*
(- Kyber DEK wrap is mandatory in lockbox mode \(no Kyber opt-out\).) Tj
T*
(- Lockbox unlock modes:) Tj
T*
(- default: password-only UX \(Kyber secret wrap stored in wallet metadata\).) Tj
T*
(- advanced: password + Kyber unlock text file import on unlock \(.txt bundle\).) Tj
T*
(- Encryption stack:) Tj
T*
(- password KDF: Argon2id) Tj
T*
(- payload cipher: AES-256-GCM) Tj
T*
(- DEK wrap: AES-256-GCM) Tj
T*
(- required PQ wrap: Kyber \(kyber1024_ref by default\) wrapping the same DEK for hybrid/PQ backup) Tj
T*
(integrity.) Tj
T*
(- Plaintext fields \(kept visible for wallet UX while locked\):) Tj
T*
(- identifier, role, network, defaults, hashed_public_key, address_base56, source/version.) Tj
T*
(- Encrypted fields:) Tj
T*
(- raw public_key / cli_public_key) Tj
T*
(- all private key parts \(f/g/F/G\)) Tj
T*
(- mnemonic fields \(mnemonic_phrase, mnemonic_words, mnemonic_text, mnemonic_meta\).) Tj
T*
(- Security metadata is stored in _wallet_security \(schema athokey-lockbox-v1\).) Tj
T*
(- Advanced-mode Kyber unlock file format:) Tj
T*
(- schema: athokey-kyber-unlock-v1) Tj
T*
(- includes strict integrity hash and binding metadata) Tj
T*
(- importer fails closed on tampered/invalid format.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
ET
endstream
endobj
